01:09.515 --> 01:10.698
Welcome to everybody.

01:10.738 --> 01:12.882
Good morning, good morning, good morning.

01:13.410 --> 01:16.655
And everybody in the overflow out there, we see you right now.

01:16.895 --> 01:19.319
