01:19.419 --> 01:22.644
So God is doing some awesome work here in our community.

01:22.685 --> 01:23.726
We're in week number two.

01:24.187 --> 01:29.976
If this is your first time here, and we're in a second week of a series called Upgrade, and we started it last week.

01:30.056 --> 01:33.842
And what we said last week is that, man, isn't it fun to upgrade stuff?

01:34.466 --> 01:43.837
We upgrade things like our phones and our cars and it's always fun to kind of get the next version or to improve things in our life or even to improve things in our homes.

01:44.378 --> 01:51.326
I remember a few years ago, Jack and I, we wanted to move, we wanted to get into a larger house because our kids were growing.

01:51.366 --> 01:57.874
We've got three teenagers and we were going to need some more parking space and we were going to need a basement for the kids to go dwelling.

01:58.146 --> 02:00.178
