02:07.876 --> 02:11.199
I'm sorry, the countertops and the floors.

02:11.479 --> 02:12.220
They were dated.

02:12.280 --> 02:16.283
And so we went ahead and upgraded the countertops and we upgraded the floors.

02:16.683 --> 02:21.388
