04:34.100 --> 04:34.982
It was God's idea.

04:35.022 --> 04:36.243
It wasn't Joshua's idea.

04:36.544 --> 04:46.296
So I challenged you to do three things last week in order to get extreme clarity, to spend time in God's word every day, to meditate on the brevity of life, and also to answer this question.

04:46.557 --> 04:47.698
How does my

04:47.810 --> 04:49.673
upgrade, impact the lives of others.

04:50.074 --> 04:51.716
It cannot just be for you, right?

04:51.756 --> 04:54.621
Those too many people in this world, God wants to bless other people.

04:54.661 --> 04:59.028
So hopefully, hopefully you came today and you have a target.

04:59.409 --> 05:01.913
You have extreme clarity on what your upgrade is.

05:01.973 --> 05:03.356
