06:08.290 --> 06:11.595
He's going to ask us to do something that we're not capable of doing ourselves.

06:11.655 --> 06:20.228
He's going to ask us to go past where we think our abilities can take us into an unknown realm.

06:21.049 --> 06:26.397
He's going to ask us to push into areas we've never been before and to do things that we've never done before.

06:26.898 --> 06:27.619
Think about it with me.

06:27.639 --> 06:31.805
God says to Joshua, Joshua, my servant Moses is dead.

06:32.486 --> 06:37.874
Now is the time for you to take my people to Israelites across the Jordan River.

06:38.306 --> 06:39.147
into the promised land.

06:39.187 --> 06:40.048
Think about that with me.

06:40.609 --> 06:46.055
You're Joshua, or maybe you're not Joshua, maybe you're just part of the 1.5 million people that make up the Israelites.

06:46.775 --> 06:49.679
And you get this instruction from Joshua, hey, we're gonna go across the Jordan River.

06:50.099 --> 06:52.502
