13:04.591 --> 13:05.272
There's no bridge.

13:05.712 --> 13:06.433
There's no boats.

13:07.094 --> 13:07.875
We have no swords.

13:07.935 --> 13:08.676
We have no armor.

13:08.896 --> 13:10.898
How once we get across, how are we going to fight?

13:12.380 --> 13:15.223
Josh, be strong and be courageous.

13:15.263 --> 13:17.906
Do not be afraid or discouraged.

13:19.010 --> 13:20.914
Because that's what happens when we go into the unknown.

13:20.954 --> 13:21.935
