13:27.626 --> 13:35.761
It's not just because of fear and doubt, but also because God is going to require Joshua and the Israelites to bring some effort in your notes.

13:35.801 --> 13:36.302
Watch this.

13:37.604 --> 13:42.834
Every upgrade involves effort from you and from God, from both of us.

13:44.354 --> 13:47.318
In other words, God is not gonna do all of the lifting for you.

13:47.338 --> 13:50.142
God is not just gonna zap you like, you know, a member in Star Trek.

13:50.162 --> 13:54.728
Those of you who remember Star Trek, God's not gonna beam you across the Jordan.

