16:12.544 --> 16:14.886
Like, maybe you say, well, the people really didn't do that much.

16:14.966 --> 16:17.348
Okay, maybe the percentages were 5% and 95%.

16:17.589 --> 16:18.329
The people did 5%.

16:18.690 --> 16:19.591
God did 95%.

16:19.671 --> 16:20.331
Okay, that's fine.

16:21.332 --> 16:22.714
But it was still something.

16:23.214 --> 16:25.977
God still requires something from you and I, doesn't he?

16:26.998 --> 16:27.538
Yes or no?

