16:32.672 --> 16:33.714
Jericho is the first city.

16:33.774 --> 16:34.695
What's it look like?

16:34.715 --> 16:37.138
Well, God comes to these your lights and says, here's what, here's the deal.

16:37.158 --> 16:38.500
