23:17.313 --> 23:18.174
Well, I'm trusting God.

23:19.336 --> 23:20.297
I'm putting my hope in God.

23:20.337 --> 23:21.278
I'm counting on God.

23:21.298 --> 23:21.499
Good.

23:22.059 --> 23:23.081
I want you to do that.

23:23.461 --> 23:24.923
