23:30.466 --> 23:39.739
Don't use it as an excuse as not to get on a budget or not to get in a small group or not to read the scriptures or not to, you know, get rid of your phone because it's causing you to, you know, look at pornography.

23:40.119 --> 23:42.843
Don't use faith as an excuse for a lack of effort.

23:42.923 --> 23:43.424
This makes sense.

23:43.504 --> 23:44.225
I'm preaching now.

23:44.645 --> 23:44.946
Come on.

23:45.827 --> 23:50.814
I know you guys don't, you don't want to be encouraged and stuff, but you know, you know, this is, this is where we got to talk and see what we got to talk about.

23:53.037 --> 23:55.360
You know, oftentimes we say, God, I'm counting on you.

23:55.400 --> 23:57.042
