23:57.442 --> 23:59.145
Good, I'm glad you're counting on me, but guess what?

23:59.285 --> 24:00.206
I'm counting on you.

24:02.209 --> 24:04.793
You bring some effort here if you wanna fix your marriage.

24:04.833 --> 24:08.519
You bring some effort here if you want your finances to get in order, if you want a better job.

24:08.539 --> 24:10.082
You bring some effort to that.

24:10.102 --> 24:11.404
Put your feet in the water.

24:11.644 --> 24:13.627
Walk around the city a couple of times.

24:15.410 --> 24:16.632
And then I'll meet you halfway.

24:17.954 --> 24:19.176
See in Augustine, put it this way.

24:20.758 --> 24:22.481
Pray as though everything depended upon God.

24:23.102 --> 24:24.063
Man, I'm telling you, pray.

24:24.744 --> 24:25.906
Hoping God, trusting God.

24:26.274 --> 24:30.319
But then on the back end, work as though everything depended upon you.

24:31.480 --> 24:32.462
Do you see the balance there?

24:33.603 --> 24:39.390
The Apostle Paul in Philippians chapter two, when he was talking about what does it look like to become a mature Christian and a mature Christ file.

24:39.410 --> 24:40.051
Listen to what he said.

24:41.293 --> 24:43.295
Work hard to show the results of your salvation.

24:45.318 --> 24:47.160
Obey God with deep reverence and fear.

24:47.761 --> 24:48.441
Like it's on you.

24:48.502 --> 24:52.146
Now on the other side of the coin, God is working in you.

24:52.322 --> 24:54.625
giving you the desire and the power to do what pleases him.

24:54.645 --> 24:55.667
Like God will meet you there.

24:55.967 --> 24:56.989
He will give you the desire.

24:57.169 --> 24:58.131
