25:18.461 --> 25:22.066
And then God will meet you there and He will give you the success that you're looking for.

25:22.786 --> 25:27.191
Every single upgrade will require effort from you and from God.

25:27.311 --> 25:31.516
How hard do you push as hard as you possibly can?

25:32.857 --> 25:38.163
God tells Joshua, Josh, you're gonna have to be strong and you're gonna have to be courageous.

25:40.285 --> 25:47.954
Wow, you're gonna ask me to do things I've never done before and go places I've never been before, fight battles I've never fought before, cross rivers.

25:49.634 --> 25:53.258
When that happens, fear comes in, doubt comes in, self-doubt, doubt in God.

25:54.640 --> 25:57.203
