26:16.727 --> 26:16.927
Ready?

26:17.508 --> 26:19.410
For the Lord your God is, say it with me.

26:19.842 --> 26:20.404
with you.

26:20.584 --> 26:21.246
I'm with you.

26:22.249 --> 26:26.763
Wherever you go, in the same way I was with Moses, I will be with you.

26:27.184 --> 26:29.671
