28:59.936 --> 29:00.977
Doesn't mean you back away.

29:01.278 --> 29:02.940
It's going to take some effort.

29:03.841 --> 29:06.625
And God will meet you there saying, ah, you're not alone in this deal.

29:07.907 --> 29:08.528
You do your part.

29:08.548 --> 29:09.289
I'll do my part.

29:09.770 --> 29:10.891
Where do you need to push the limit?

