33:14.658 --> 33:17.623
You're the one that's gonna take this deal to the next level.

33:18.245 --> 33:18.725
You're the one.

33:18.745 --> 33:19.326
Say this with me.

33:19.347 --> 33:20.028
I'm the one.

33:20.068 --> 33:21.350
Say, I'm the one.

33:21.791 --> 33:23.234
Not in a prideful way, okay?

33:23.274 --> 33:27.041
I'm not trying to say, you're God or I'm God or we could, but in a responsible way.

33:27.141 --> 33:27.942
