33:56.135 --> 34:00.722
Pray as though everything depended upon God and work as though everything depended upon you.

34:00.802 --> 34:05.486
Now, some of you here today, you need to hear this last thought I have about the Ark of the Covenant.

34:05.506 --> 34:06.507
