34:12.713 --> 34:17.558
The presence of God dwelled on top of the Ark in this place called the Mercy Seat between the two Golden Angels.

34:18.179 --> 34:20.201
Guess what else was significant about the Ark?

34:20.881 --> 34:30.130
When they got it across, when they set up the tent, when they set up even in the future tabernacle, the Ark of the Covenant was in the middle of the tabernacle, the centerpiece.

34:30.306 --> 34:32.849
They called it the holy of holies, the inner sanctuary.

34:32.909 --> 34:40.376
And once a year, once a year, the high priest would go in to the holy of holies and take the blood of a spotless lamb.

34:41.177 --> 34:42.558
And he would sprinkle that blood.

34:42.598 --> 34:48.464
I know it sounds gross, but he would take that blood and he would sprinkle it over the top of the mercy sheet right where the presence of God was.

34:49.065 --> 34:49.866
You know why he did that?

34:51.427 --> 34:53.169
To atone for the nation's sins.

34:55.752 --> 34:58.194
Without the shedding of blood, there's no forgiveness of sin.

34:59.138 --> 35:01.901
Somebody's got to pay for all the wrongdoing in all the sin.

35:02.522 --> 35:08.469
So once a year they would have toned for the whole nation's sins by sprinkling the blood on that spot of the Ark of the Covenant.

35:08.489 --> 35:09.310
You know what Jesus did?

35:10.231 --> 35:12.254
Many many years later he would spread out his arms.

35:12.554 --> 35:14.817
The perfect spotless sinless Lamb of God.

35:15.197 --> 35:16.118
He would be slain.

35:16.499 --> 35:22.386
He would be crucified so that your sin and my sin and the sin of the entire world

35:23.138 --> 35:24.800
could be atoned, could be forgiven.

35:25.040 --> 35:33.951
Did you know that you can step into a relationship right now because of what Christ did on the cross 2,000 years ago and He shed His blood for you and He did it because He loved you?

35:34.551 --> 35:39.718
Jesus said this one time, there's no greater love than for a person to lay down His life for His friends and then He did it.

35:40.819 --> 35:41.880
He shed His blood for you.

35:42.140 --> 35:50.290
He died in your place and today some of you need to upgrade your life by asking Christ to save you from your sins and asking His Spirit to come live inside of you.

35:50.690 --> 35:54.276
And if you feel like you need to do that right now, this is your moment to upgrade your life.

35:54.576 --> 35:55.678
