36:13.866 --> 36:14.947
Say this, dear Jesus.

36:16.910 --> 36:19.314
Thank you for dying on the cross.

36:20.578 --> 36:24.584
for spilling your blood to cover my sin.

36:27.328 --> 36:41.669
I believe you not only died, but you came back to life, conquering the penalty, the shame, and the guilt of sin.

36:41.689 --> 36:42.590
I receive you today.

36:44.373 --> 36:44.994
