36:49.730 --> 36:55.516
Fill my heart, my soul, right now with your spirit.

36:57.419 --> 37:11.854
Upgrade my life and teach me from this point forward to love you, to honor you, and to obey you.

37:11.874 --> 37:14.277
I pray this in Jesus' name.

37:14.297 --> 37:15.058
And everybody said,

37:15.842 --> 37:16.864
Amen, amen.

37:16.884 --> 37:18.166
Can we give God glory to her?

37:18.707 --> 37:19.969
Come on, nice and loud, amen.

